Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER to resubmission leading to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time spent in process from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time taken for a case to reach Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Maximum time taken for a case to reach Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR and Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time to reach Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR for cases that were initially rejected by any approver
Metric: the average of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER to next Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
